data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Groveland, FL! This recently renovated, spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is now available for rent, offering the perfect blend of modern luxury and comfortable living.

Key Features:

Bedrooms: 4
Bathrooms: 2
Location: Groveland, FL
Availability: Ready for immediate move-in
Rent: $2,400/month

Property Highlights:

Modern Kitchen: Enjoy cooking in the brand-new, fully equipped kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space.

Spacious Bedrooms: Four generously sized bedrooms provide plenty of space for both rest and relaxation. The master suite includes a private bathroom for added convenience.

Renovated Bathrooms: Experience the luxury of updated bathrooms with contemporary fixtures and finishes, providing a spa-like atmosphere.

Open Concept Living: The home boasts an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family.

Natural Light: Abundant windows throughout the home allow for plenty of natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere.

Outdoor Living: Take advantage of the Florida sunshine in your private backyard. The property includes a patio or deck for outdoor dining and relaxation.

Ample Storage: The home offers ample storage space, including closets in each bedroom and additional storage areas throughout.

Pet-Friendly: Pets are welcome! The property is pet-friendly, allowing you to bring your furry friends along to enjoy the spacious surroundings.

Location:

Situated in the charming community of Groveland, this home is conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options. With easy access to major highways, commuting to nearby cities is a breeze.

Application Process:

Application fee: $100 per applicant
Deposit: One month's rent, security deposit and admin fee
Lease term: 12 months 

Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully renovated house your home!
